long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
🚀 Effortlessly extract Propertyfinder sale/rent real estate properties data from the list search page to a Excel/CSV/JSON/HTML/XML file.

🔧 How it Works:
1️⃣ Go to the propertyfinder listing search page.
2️⃣ Perform a search, then click the "Start" button on extension popup.
3️⃣ Choose to download from the data scraping pop-up or the task list on extension.

🌳 What data can I extract using this tool?
id, category_id, property_type, price, title, location, images, agent, broker, is_verified, is_direct_from_developer, is_new_construction, is_available, is_featured, is_premium, is_new_insert, utilities_price_type, live_viewing, is_community_expert, is_cts, bedrooms, bathrooms, size, share_url, details_path, reference, listed_date, contact_options, images_count, amenities, completion_status, furnished, property_type_id, has_view_360, rsp, rss, qs, is_exclusive, is_broker_project_property, rera, offering_type, video_url, is_smart_ad, is_spotlight_listing, is_claimed_by_agent, is_under_offer_by_competitor, listing_level, listing_level_label, location_tree, description, amenity_names, payment_method, lead_value.

Note: This extension is an independent creation and is not affiliated with or endorsed by Propertyfinder❗️🔒
